                                </div>

                                <div class="mypage_coupon_info frame400">
                                    <h3>쿠폰<img src="/images/coupon_ico.png" alt="쿠폰 아이콘"></h3>
                                    <p>0개<span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span></p>
